{"tid":1385074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務卿：香港抗議恰當 籲中国做正確的事","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:17:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":125,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6252906733e6e51f8ea675b0ecd6491d5515c7bc","tid":1385074,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpel9Hhu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpel9Hhu.jpg&h=9afb1b43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n香港「反送中」抗爭持續延燒，已經持續了2個月。美國國務卿龐皮歐說，香港民眾的抗議是恰當的，呼籲中國政府尊重香港。<br />\n<br />\n龐皮歐29日與華盛頓經濟俱樂部（ The Economic Club of Washington D.C.）主席魯班斯坦（David Rubenstein）對話時，被問到如果中國派兵到香港鎮壓示威活動，美國會有什麼回應？龐皮歐並沒有直接回答問題，僅表示「我從不回答我們將要做什麼，或不做什麼的假設」。<br />\n<br />\n龐皮歐接著說，美國非常清楚香港民眾抗議是恰當的，抗議也在美國隨處可見，像是他坐車前往國務院的路上時常遇到抗議，美國希望中方能做出正確的事，尊重香港及其有關協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2867830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2867830&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=4c930b39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2867830&h=157e5820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2867830</a>"},{"pid":"38ec85b544d978461a520869c4a19ee8bdf13da9","tid":1385074,"uid":322,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"美國非常清楚香港民眾抗議是恰當的，抗議也在美國隨處可見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9a989872e1d46a80fed55b44918955de9aa1af","tid":1385074,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97917be89ecf91d12f5706d095ec865726cdb18c","tid":1385074,"uid":17506,"like":8