/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"你試下係美國咁做吖喇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a4fd94f1c8a4133f62ed5a697ff1105d87695e","tid":1385074,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"全民8月5曰大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"fdee64ed03c159a79eb949f25d9b194c8c136aad","tid":1385074,"uid":35507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"🇺🇸🇺🇸"},{"pid":"b68a95990ab6ec40be61b64c008a042c37e8a9f8","tid":1385074,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97917be89ecf91d12f5706d095ec865726cdb18c","tid":1385074,"uid":17506,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"38ec85b544d978461a520869c4a19ee8bdf13da9","tid":1385074,"uid":322,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"美國非常清楚香港民眾抗議是恰當的，抗議也在美國隨處可見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"多謝海外巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7fde00600d9a4fc4b8aedf13ed91b51d92e9e4","tid":1385074,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"又話美警會開槍殺人,藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6217ec12adc550e0f23e198b9649798d68695a5","tid":1385074,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970486eb7a14ac29f74ab272b47a4171456b2534","tid":1385074,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7fde00600d9a4fc4b8aedf13ed91b51d92e9e4","tid":1385074,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"又話美警會開槍殺人,藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"用美國標準既話<br />\n香港班黑警死撚曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0